Introduction

Jo, born Kim Junseong, is a South Korean dancer and rapper. He is a former member of the boy group DXMON.

Jo debuted as the maknae, dancer and rapper of DXMON on January 17, 2024, with the mini album Hyperspace. However, on June 11, 2024, he went on a hiatus due to health concerns. Subsequently, on September 29, 2024, H Music Entertainment announced that Jo would be concluding his activities as a member of DXMON.
